Package com.robinpowered.sdk.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ApiResponseModel
    An interface that should be implemented by all models that represent remote API models.
    FreeBusy
    An interface for Free-busy information returned for different models.
    IdentifiableApiResponseModel<IdType>
    An interface to be implemented by models that contain an id attribute.
    Identifier
    Interface for identifiers of Devices.
    Invitable
    Interface for models that may be invited to an Event.
